                <td bgColor="#ECECEC"><textarea cols="48" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL" onselect="storeCaret(this);" onclick="storeCaret(this);" onkeyup="storeCaret(this);" onchange="storeCaret(this);">[quote][i]Originally posted by Banez Wight[/i]
[br]On Enrage,

This will cause the mob to automatically riposte ALL frontal attacks.  If you hit it from the front, it does no damageinstead the mob gets a free attack on you.  If you hit from behind, or slightly to the side you can still do damage to the mob.

On Rampage,

I have never seen the Rampage tank outside of melee distance, I couldnt tell you if the mob selects another person or just stops rampage all together.

